.\pages\acceptinvite\BUGS.md:11:- **Description:** Already-accepted invite branch redirected any token holder to staff/cabinet page without checking auth or verifying user identity.
.\pages\acceptinvite\BUGS.md:13:- **Fix:** Moved auth check before already_accepted. Added `link.invited_user !== user.id` verification.
.\pages\acceptinvite\BUGS.md:41:- **Fix:** Always use `setError(t('acceptinvite.error.generic'))`.
.\pages\acceptinvite\BUGS.md:52:### BUG-AI-007 | P2 | Race condition ΓÇö concurrent processInvite calls
.\pages\acceptinvite\BUGS.md:83:- **Description:** Edge case: if `invite_accepted_at` set but `invited_user` null (data corruption), link could be re-accepted by different user.
.\pages\acceptinvite\BUGS.md:84:- **Fix:** Check `invite_accepted_at` alone as evidence of prior acceptance.
